  m_Name: Shooting
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  header: Shooting
  description: "To shoot, start by switching to Shoot Mode using the button in the
    bottom left corner of the screen. Once in Shoot Mode, move your mouse to aim
    at your target. When you're ready, press the left mouse button to fire. Remember,
    each shot consumes one bullet. Be cautious\u2014if you\u2019re too close to a
    barrel and within its explosion radius, you\u2019ll take damage and lose health."
